Key Takeaways:

Consumer groups enable horizontal scaling of message processing
Kafka automatically rebalances partitions when consumers join or leave
Each partition is consumed by exactly one consumer in a group
Monitoring consumer lag is critical for production systems
Offset management strategies affect message processing guarantees
